overview: Kalea captivates her audience with story after story about growing up black and what it's really like chasing her dreams in the city of angels. From learning the crucial differences between arguing with crack-heads and meth-heads, to being on set and her affinity for her trusty Yorkie, Rolo TheDog McNeill, Kalea offers a hilariously honest take on black lesbian life on the road towards success.
title: Kalea McNeill: Sma'am
